Madagascar’s Inflation Rate Falls to 9.4% in July From 9.6%, Agency Says

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-08-19T12:41:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-19/madagascar-s-inflation-rate-falls-to-9-4-in-july-from-9-6-agency-says.html
Madagascar’s annual inflation rate
declined to 9.4 percent in July from 9.6 percent a month
earlier, the country’s statistics agency said.  Prices increased 0.4 percent in the month as food costs
rose, the Antananarivo-based Institut National de la Statistique
said in a statement e-mailed today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
